                <head>205. Summary of Conclusions of a Mini-Special Coordination Committee
                        Meeting<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d205fn1">Source: Carter Library,
                        National Security Affairs, Staff Material, North/South, <persName
                            corresp="#p_PRA_1">Pastor</persName>, Country, Box 26, Jamaica, 3/80.
                        Secret. The meeting was held in the White House Situation Room.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            from="1980-03-26T11:40:00-05:00" to="1980-03-26T12:40:00-05:00">March
                            26, 1980, 11:40 a.m.–12:40 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <list type="subject">
                    <head>SUBJECT</head>
                    <item>Jamaica, El Salvador and Suriname (S)</item>
                </list>
                <list type="participants">
                    <head>PARTICIPANTS</head>
                    <item>
